CROQUE MONSIEUR CROISSANT LASAGNA

INGREDIENTS
* 	10 shop-bought all-butter croissants
* 	a little butter for greasing
* 	1 1/2 cups bechamel sauce
* 	2 cups grated emmental cheese
* 	10 slices wafer thin cooked ham, plus a little more for layering
* 	nutmeg, a scrape
* 	dijon mustard, 1/2 tsp per croissant

CROQUE MONSIEUR MASH BALLS
INGREDIENTS
* 6 cups cold leftover mash
* 4 slices ham, chopped into small cubes
* 3 cups grated emmental
* 2 tbsp dijon mustard
* 1/4 cup finely chopped parsley
* 1 tbsp salt
* 1 tbsp pepper
* 1 cup flour
* 4 eggs, beaten with a little milk
* 2 cups panko breadcrumbs
* Enough groundnut oil to deep fry

node.text:
Comfort in a bowl - a BREAD bowl! 🍞 
Spaghetti Meatball Soup in a Garlic Bread Bowl - Come and Spaghet it 🍝 

INGREDIENTS
Spaghetti Meatball Soup Bowls
Meatballs:
400g Beef Mince
300g Pork Mince
½ cup bread crumbs
1 egg, whisked
2 cloves garlic, minced
2 tbsp chopped parsley
¼ cup finely grated parmesan
½ tsp oregano
½ tsp salt
½ tsp pepper
Diced yellow cheddar
Oil
 
3 tsp oil
1 white onion, diced
2 cloves garlic, minced
½ tsp chilli flakes
1 tsp oregano
1 tbsp tomato paste
600ml passata
4 cups chicken stock
2 cups water
½ tsp salt
½ tsp pepper
225g dry spaghetti
 
Large sourdough boule

•
#bread #breadbowl #comfortfood #meatballs #spaghetti #goodsoup #goodrecipe #autumn #autumnrecipe

Buffalo Chicken 
Butter 65g
Hot water 0.9 cups
Flour 2 cups
Salt, big pinch
Handful of chives, finely chopped
1 chicken breast, shredded
½ cup hot sauce 
½ cup Butter, melted
1 tsp Garlic powder 
Blue cheese ranch, to serve
